{"tid":1194540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報: Google地圖竟標示反修例遊行時間地點外國勢力滲透","createTime":"2019-06-09T10:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T08:07:41.000Z","uid":160028,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6248b9c83d51f6ee6630f6a2523dea3cf94491b1","tid":1194540,"uid":160028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2019/0609/300873.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fhongkong%2Ftext%2F2019%2F0609%2F300873.html&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=4d385998\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/hongkong/text/2019/0609/300873.html</a><br />\n笑撚左笑撚埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985f558a51d5098eff81205b6e06c6ca41fdc7d8","tid":1194540,"uid":160028,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"大公文匯全媒體報道：香港反對派組織今日（9日）下午發起反對修改移交逃犯條例「大遊行」，Google地圖在遊行集合起點位置維多利亞公園標示出相關字樣。時事分析專家認為，此舉證明遊行背後或有外國勢力操弄，與「港奸」一起瘋狂催谷遊行人數。<br />\n<br />\n  近年香港政治爭議，背後總會看到美英等外國勢力的存在。據港體不完全統計，今年以來，外國政府和政客針對香港事務的公開干涉事件至少有15次，平均每月至少三次。<br />\n<br />\n  （大公文匯全媒體新聞中心供稿）"},{"pid":"b1c35db6b2c25bf81330a6a4c1f059da02cd9f13","tid":1194540,"uid":49359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"仲以為出膠post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a4fa317a950d0d96eecd469760d50bc5a13780","tid":1194540,"uid":40826,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"真係弱撚智"},{"pid":"a01bacdf822f426e023c415b08b21bd337f55a23","tid":1194540,"uid":39660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"佢以為啲pin係人手加落去？"},{"pid":"6ee1687f836f206fa4a0b558dbc0a842ded5b69d","t